{"tid":52539,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南港島綫】「廢青」噩耗 港鐵新設優先𨋢","createTime":"2016-12-24T07:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T07:07:59.000Z","uid":16016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de1170ccd98f727acbde37db17255db1a528849f","tid":52539,"uid":16016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:01:43.000Z","msg":"[轉自蘋果日報]<br />\n港鐵優先座問題已甚惹爭議，今次南港鐵綫通車，港鐵更新引入「優先𨋢」，車站內前往大堂的電梯全部貼上紅色優先使用貼紙，供有需要人士優先使用。港鐵車務營運總管李聖基指，由於車站有多條扶手梯前往各層，因而考慮引入優先使用電梯方便有需要人士使用。<br />\n<br />\n李聖基又指，金鐘站現有荃灣綫及港島綫月台的擴建位置，今日雖仍落下防火閘及以膠布圍封，主要是因有關位置可通往擴建部分，需要在周三南港島綫通車時同步啟用。他又強調，車站工程經已全部完成，可於通車日全部啟用。<br />\n<br />\n另外，早前南港島綫列車在測試期間曾經死機，李強調列車所有大問題已處理，目前尚餘輕微調較作正進行，如令列車停站更準確。他又指，南港島綫車站始終按中型鐵路規模設計，會密切留意人流問題，各站會有人流管制措施對應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161224&amp;guid=56087474&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161224%26guid%3D56087474%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=wWkvSZmSekpofuy52BZ%2BhoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=9c4b52b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161224%26guid%3D56087474%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=fafd33ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161224&amp;guid=56087474&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"05a0cd1e80d6cc29dd33b85fd4fcd19d72f582e0","tid":52539,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}